headline: Raymond James Ltd. Appoints Eric Lauzon as Senior Vice President, Growth and Development
summary: Raymond James Ltd., Canada's largest independent financial services firm, is pleased to announce the appointment of Eric Lauzon as Senior Vice President, Growth and Development, effective September 2, 2025.
